programme.title: Vegetables, But Delicious
programme.desc: Grilling is the perfect way to imbue your veggies with deliciousness. Chef Dale crafts a family style platter of trumpet mushrooms, eggplant marinated in spicy ssam jang, and charred yellow squash served with a green goddess dressing.

programme.title: Kabobs and Skewers
programme.desc: Kabobs and skewers are a family tradition for Chef Dale. This Mediterranean-inspired meal features beef and shrimp kabobs with grilled tomatoes, potatoes, and eggplant, all served on warm pita with a tangy white sauce.

programme.title: End of Summer Seafood Feast
programme.desc: The end of summer is near, and Chef Dale goes out in style with a giant seafood feast! Lobster, crab, clams, shrimp, and scallops, all served directly on the table with plenty of buttery garlic bread. Thanks for watching, and until we grill again!

programme.title: Summer Surf 'n' Turf
programme.desc: Chef Dale Talde kicks lobster & steak to the curb as he puts a Spanish-style spin on your typical surf ‘n’ turf by creating Pork & Clams, Lobster and Mushroom Fideos, and Tomato & Tuna Bread then washing it all down with a tasty Michelada.

programme.title: Perfectly Prepared Steaks
programme.desc: Big Daddy Dale Talde shows you how to marinate, prep, & grill up the biggest and best steaks out there. From a Hanger Steak with Salsa Verde to a Ribeye with Ginger Chili Relish, and tops it all off with the father of all steaks… The Porterhouse.

programme.title: Christmas In July
programme.desc: It’s July on the calendar but Christmas in our hearts. Frankie whips up three summertime twists on Christmas themed dishes and serves up tips and tricks for celebrating the most wonderful time of year in July.

programme.title: We Knead Pizza
programme.desc: Cancel the pizza delivery, it’s time to save money and build your pies from scratch. With three different pizza styles, you’re bound to find one that satisfies your craving without digging into your wallet.

programme.title: Pho, Poke, & Pig in O’ahu
programme.desc: Frankie explores Hawaii's O’ahu island to get nourished from fresh tuna poke, heartfelt Pho, and hand-pounded poi.

programme.title: Quail, Alligator Sausage, & Gumbo in New Orleans
programme.desc: Frankie stops by New Orleans to chow down on lacquered quail, a beast of a Po Boy, and Creole Beef Daube.

programme.title: Cubanos, Empanadas, & Smoked Beef Rib in Miami
programme.desc: Frankie goes to Miami to sample serious cherry smoked beef rib, three cheese spinach empanadas, and a legendary Cubano sandwich with homemade mustard.

programme.title: Chiles, Burgers, & Tenderloins in Santa Fe
programme.desc: Frankie heads to Santa Fe investigating New Mexican cuisines eating green chili burgers, poblano chile stews, and sweet blue-corn pancakes.

programme.title: Apocalypse Burgers
programme.desc: Chef Dale Talde kicks the summer off right with a burger blowout featuring Brisket Burgers with Grilled Onions and Blue Cheese, Shrimp Burgers with XO Sauce and a Fried Egg, and Lamb Sliders with Feta Ranch and don’t forget the Lemon Oregano Fries.

programme.title: Sausage Egg & Cheese All Day Long
programme.desc: Chef Dale Talde brings out the best of brunch with sweet and savory hits such as Bacon Wrapped Dates Stuffed with Chorizo, Maple Sausage, Egg, & Cheese Fried Rice, and the tastiest BBQ Duck, Egg, & Corn Scallion Pancake Sandwiches you’ve ever eaten.

programme.title: Summer Surf 'n' Turf
programme.desc: Chef Dale Talde kicks lobster & steak to the curb as he puts a Spanish-style spin on your typical surf ‘n’ turf by creating Pork & Clams, Lobster and Mushroom Fideos, and Tomato & Tuna Bread then washing it all down with a tasty Michelada.

programme.title: Perfectly Prepared Steaks
programme.desc: Big Daddy Dale Talde shows you how to marinate, prep, & grill up the biggest and best steaks out there. From a Hanger Steak with Salsa Verde to a Ribeye with Ginger Chili Relish, and tops it all off with the father of all steaks… The Porterhouse.

programme.title: Pizza Party on the Grill
programme.desc: It’s Pizza Time! Chef Dale Talde grills up amazing pizzas for every palate including a Detroit Style Pie, a Cheddar Naan Pie with a Spiced Chick Peas & Potatoes, and gives your childhood favorite French Bread Pizza a much needed upgrade.

programme.title: Grill These Sandwiches
programme.desc: Mad Good Food Host Derrell Smith joins Chef Dale Talde at the grill as they cook up some stupendous sandwiches including a Salmon Pastrami Reuben, a Meatball Banh Mi, and even some Grilled Ice Cream Sandwiches.

programme.title: New Orleans-Style Shrimp & Oysters
programme.desc: Chef Dale Talde brings us to the bayou as he creates a NOLA-inspired menu complete with Chargrilled Oysters, Black Pepper Shrimp Po’boys, finishes it off with Bananas Foster, and washes it all down with a Fruity Grilled Hurricane.

programme.title: Sunday Vietnamese Brisket with Noodles
programme.desc: Chef Dale Talde shows us how he does Sunday up right as he grills up some Vietnamese Brisket with Rice Noodles, Crispy Swordfish Summer Rolls, and tops it all off with some tasty Soju Floats. Hey, it’s Sunday somewhere, right?

programme.title: Beer Brats & BBQ Ribs
programme.desc: Chef Dale Talde grills up summer favorites perfect for any backyard BBQ. Cheddar beer brats in a pretzel bun, BBQ lamb ribs with Chinese mustard sauce, watermelon lime soju punch, & warm donuts with grilled strawberries & whipped cream for dessert.

programme.title: Bougie Badass Burgers
programme.desc: Chef Dale Talde brings your basic burgers to a new level with his dry-aged beef burger with potatoes and truffle dijon mayo, a part-beef part-pork belly burger with cheddar & an egg, and lastly a crispy mushroom tortilla burger with salsa & cheese.

programme.title: Party for Pennies
programme.desc: Frankie makes three dishes for a party of four, that when combined, are cheaper than just one meal out for brunch. Then, it's a taco party for five people for only $20!

programme.title: Food Back from the Dead
programme.desc: Stale bread, old bananas, canned food, dry foods... they've all gotten a bad wrap, but this is not the end of them yet! Don't let this stuff sit in the pantry, don't let it go to waste - Frankie encourages you to stretch further and cheaper!

programme.title: Wrap it Up!
programme.desc: First, Frankie packs a one-two punch of bargain and nutrition with butternut squash in three nostalgic, old school dishes. Then he shows you how to prep portable wraps at home for easy, peasey lunches.

programme.title: Bacon My Heart
programme.desc: Versatility is important. These three items - bacon, eggs, and a whole chicken - will feed you a plethora of delicious meals... and for cheap!

programme.title: Instant Gratification
programme.desc: Everyone loves carbs! Endlessly versatile, cheap, and super filling - Frankie shows you tricks for pasta, pizza dough, and delicious, easy ramen meals that aren't soup.

programme.title: Cauliflower's Star Power
programme.desc: Cauliflower is a star and can be transformed into unexpected dishes. Plus it's delicious and nutritious! Frankie reminds us to buy dried-goods in bulk and makes a big chuck roast that stretches over three dishes.

programme.title: Traveling for Your Tastebuds
programme.desc: You don't have to travel half way around the world to try a different cuisine - Italian and Filipino foods are accessible right here, right now.

programme.title: Street Food Faves at Home
programme.desc: Frankie makes street food at home. It's fresher, healthier, and cheaper! Then - get ready! - because you've never seen rice like this before.

programme.title: Sweet on You
programme.desc: Sweet potatoes and a sweet tooth - Frankie's got you covered on the cheap and full of nutrition. Some times, you've got to indulge!

programme.title: Save Dough, Make Dough
programme.desc: Prepping meals at home is cheaper and way more nutritious! Frankie makes portable breakfasts for the work week and forays into the stuffed dough of different cultures.

programme.title: Going With the Grain
programme.desc: Frankie teaches you how to prep ingredients to make delicious, healthy meals for a fraction of the time and cost.

programme.title: Fancy Free
programme.desc: Going to the movies is expensive! Frankie shows us how to make a delicious TV dinner, popcorn, and dessert for less money than a movie ticket! Then, French food isn’t all fancy and expensive. These are meals big on flavor and light on your wallet!

programme.title: Royal Documentaries - S01:E28 - Diana And Sarah The Royal Wives Of Windsor Part 2
programme.desc: 威爾士公主黛安娜和約克公爵夫人莎拉均嫁入女王的大家族，處於丑聞中心卻以不同方式離開。可惜的是，黛安娜已去世，而莎拉幸存下來，重新開始。隨著時間推移，她們的奮鬥可以得到更好的理解，本紀錄片探討了這些挑戰...

programme.title: Royal Documentaries - S01:E42 - Diana A Model Princess
programme.desc: Diana's fashion sense was something people often looked at closely. She had a knack for picking outfits that were both stylish and sophisticated, which always grabbed attention. Her hats were another standout feature; she often wore elegant designs that added a touch of grace to her look. Her hair was also iconic, usually styled neatly with a slight bounce, perfectly framing her face and adding to her elegant appearance.

programme.title: Carter's W.A.R. - S02:E01 - At All Costs
programme.desc: Ivan emprende un viaje para salvar a los diecinueve rinocerontes de su amigo de la epidemia de caza furtiva que azota Sudáfrica. La solución: la pesadilla logística de transportar a toda la manada a un lugar seguro a 600 millas al otro lado del país.

programme.title: Alaska's Ultimate Bush Pilots - S02:E03 - Salvage: Gone-Awry
programme.desc: Joel y Mark Barker tientan a la suerte y vuelan a tierra de nadie para encontrar y salvar un avión blanco en un bosque nevado mientras luchan contra la hipotermia por el camino.

programme.title: Alaska's Ultimate Bush Pilots - S02:E04 - Heaven at 5000 Feet
programme.desc: El piloto Josiah Freeman lleva al snowboarder profesional Mark Barajas a la cima de las montañas Chugach para practicar un heliesquí infernal.

programme.title: Wardens - S01:E05 - Operation Cascade
programme.desc: 上密蘇里河是釣魚和漂流的最佳地點。在第4區的凱斯凱德區域，有關於私人財產上一輛奇怪的露營車的謠言。在第7區，他們忙於進行水安全檢查。

programme.title: Wardens - S01:E06 - Operation Blackfoot
programme.desc: Wardens in Region 2 are checking out a Tip Mont report about several elk down in an area known for grizzlies. When they get there, one elk and the suspect aren't around. Meanwhile, wardens in Region 7 are dealing with gunfire during a decoy sting operation.

programme.title: Fight to Survive - S02:E05 - Stranded in the Alaska Wilderness Part 1
programme.desc: Los cazadores Adrian Knopps y Garrett Hagen se aventuran en la parte más remota del fiordo Misty de Alaska, cazando alces y osos. Tras una exitosa cacería, Adrian se ve atrapado por una marejada de seis metros después de que Garrett no regrese con el esquife.

programme.title: Fight to Survive - S02:E06 - Stranded in the Alaska Wilderness Part 2

programme.desc: Tras una exitosa cacería, el compañero de caza de Adrian Knopps desaparece llevándose el oso al barco. Ahora Adrian se encuentra varado en una llanura rodeado de osos y manadas de lobos y con una enorme tormenta que se cierne sobre él. ¿Cómo sobrevivirá?

programme.title: Jim Shockey's Uncharted - S01:E06 - Heaven's Gate
programme.desc: Kyrgyzstan. Jim and Corey journey to the Tian Shan mountain range in search of high altitude mountain dwelling sheep and ibex.

programme.title: Savage Wild - S05:E05 - The Clewiston Terror
programme.desc: Un enorme jabalí está aterrorizando a los trabajadores de una granja en Clewiston, Florida. Manny es llamado para llevar al cerdo ante la justicia.

programme.title: Savage Wild - S05:E06 - Wild Boar Naples
programme.desc: Manny caza jabalíes con su lanza tridente.

programme.title: Savage Wild - S05:E07 - Slaying the Port Labelle Monster
programme.desc: Manny se enreda con un cerdo monstruoso en los densos bosques de Port Labelle.

programme.title: Savage Wild - S05:E08 - Save a Watermelon Kill a Boar Part 1
programme.desc: Manny sigue la pista de un jabalí que asalta campos de sandías en el suroeste de Florida.

programme.title: Wild Ones - S01:E11 - Most Poisonous
programme.desc: You wouldn’t want to be bitten by any of these but which one has the deadliest poison? The venom from the most poisonous snake on the planet? A rare poisonous lizard? Or is it the blue ringed octopus?

programme.title: Wild Ones - S01:E12 - Migration
programme.desc: Los animales, grandes y no tan grandes, recorren cientos de kilómetros, algunos en busca de comida, otros para encontrar el lugar ideal para reproducirse. Desde las cebras que atraviesan las sabanas africanas hasta los enormes viajes que emprenden las tortugas para encontrar la playa perfecta donde desovar, los viajes anuales, a menudo peligrosos, son simplemente alucinantes.

programme.title: Wild Ones - S01:E13 - Who is the King?
programme.desc: Se calcula que hay aproximadamente 8,7 millones de especies diferentes de animales en la Tierra. Cada una de ellas ha desarrollado técnicas y habilidades de supervivencia únicas, específicas y a menudo mortales. ¿Cómo elegir un favorito entre un abanico tan amplio de criaturas espectaculares y hermosas?

programme.title: Sasquatch Mountain Man - S01:E01 - British Colombia Moose
programme.desc: Conoce a Laramy Sasquatch Miller, uno de los últimos hombres de montaña de las Montañas Rocosas. Laramy Sasquatch Miller, de ascendencia india y entrenado por auténticos montañeses, sólo utiliza un arco hecho a mano y un rifle Hawken tradicional del calibre 54 para recorrer la ruta de los montañeses. Desde las profundidades de las Rocosas canadienses hasta las llanuras del Medio Oeste, cazando, cazando con trampas y sobreviviendo de la tierra.

programme.title: Miracles of Nature - S01:E12 - Naturally Vibrant
programme.desc: El sur de Moravia, en la República Checa, alberga una gran variedad de hermosas orquídeas. Desde allí nos dirigimos al Caribe, a Cuba, con sus vistas de increíble belleza contrastadas con brutales peleas de gallos. De Cuba viajamos a Fiyi, en el Océano Pacífico, a menudo considerado un verdadero paraíso en la Tierra.

programme.title: Miracles of Nature - S01:E13 - Naturally Hewn
programme.desc: En este episodio viajamos del Sur al Norte de Tierra Santa, Israel, deteniéndonos para admirar las vistas y empaparnos de la importancia bíblica de los lugares históricos. Continuamos hacia los Altos del Golán, en el Norte, donde el conflicto reciente sigue siendo muy evidente, y concluimos nuestra peregrinación en las orillas de Galilea.

programme.title: Miracles of Nature - S02:E01 - Naturally Wild
programme.desc: Muchas islas se encuentran en el mar entre Gran Bretaña y Escandinavia. Todas estas islas habrían permanecido cubiertas de nieve y la vida no habría sido sostenible de no ser por la Corriente del Golfo. Las aguas cálidas que fluyen por el Océano Atlántico hasta Sudamérica explican el clima templado de las islas, su rica naturaleza y una historia que se remonta miles de años atrás. Así son las tres islas que vamos a visitar hoy en Milagros de la Naturaleza: Vesterålen, la Isla Justa y las Orcadas.

programme.title: Miracles of Nature - S02:E02- Naturally Noble
programme.desc: Zimbabue era inicialmente Rodesia del Sur y se encuentra al sur de las cataratas Victoria, junto al río Zambeze. Zambia era inicialmente Rodesia del Norte y se encuentra en la otra orilla del río. Zimbabue es un país sin salida al mar situado en el sureste de África. Limita al sur con Sudáfrica. Según los arqueólogos, los primeros registros indican que los primeros asentamientos humanos en esta zona se remontan al siglo III.

programme.title: Royal Documentaries - S01:E43 - Diana A Day In The Life
programme.desc: 當戴安娜訂婚時，她始終處於媒體的視野中。她在一生中專注於自己的兒子，並致力於慈善工作，例如對地雷發表意見。戴安娜利用自己的名氣來引起人們對這些和其他重要問題的關注。這部經過深思熟慮的節目更深入地研究了20世紀最驚人的人物之一。通過前所未見的畫面，它展示了她從一個害羞的少女走到成為威爾士公主戴安娜的歷程，包括她最後日子的感人時刻。

programme.title: Carter's W.A.R. - S02:E02 - The Heart of the Conflict
programme.desc: Investigando una serie de leones asesinados, Ivan llega al corazón mismo de un antiguo conflicto entre humanos y leones. El resultado pondrá a prueba los propios valores fundamentales de Ivan sobre la cultura

programme.title: Alaska's Ultimate Bush Pilots - S02:E05 - Hanging by a Thread
programme.desc: Los pilotos de Tanalian Aviation Joel y Josiah se ganan la vida transportando una máquina de nieve varada.

programme.title: Alaska's Ultimate Bush Pilots - S02:E06 - Into The Deep
programme.desc: Los pilotos de bush tienen que utilizar todas sus habilidades -buceo, aparejo submarino y vuelo experto- para intentar salvar un ala de de Havilland Beaver en el fondo del lago 6 Mile.

programme.title: Wardens - S01:E07 - Operation Spotted Dog
programme.desc: Working to protect our treasured natural resources in some of the country's most secluded spots means there's never a boring day on the job.

programme.title: Wardens - S01:E08 - Operation Boat Float
programme.desc: In the shade of the wild mountains, the Yellowstone River transforms into a colorful spectacle during the yearly boat float weekend. Armed with jet boats, the Wardens gear up for a wild time, looking out for the river and helping out the wacky rafters.

programme.title: Fight to Survive - S02:E07 - The Journal
programme.desc: El pastor Mike Turner está haciendo una excursión en solitario a través de la divisoria continental en la implacable cordillera Wind Rivers de Wyoming cuando queda irremediablemente atrapado bajo una roca. En su diario relata su agotadora lucha de 11 días por sobrevivir.

programme.title: Fight to Survive - S02:E08 - Tree Stand Fall
programme.desc: El cazador de ciervos Nathan Holcomb cae en picado desde su puesto en el árbol. La peor pesadilla de cualquier cazador se convierte en la realidad de Nathan. Con la espalda rota y paralizado, Nathan debe arrastrarse por su cuenta para encontrar ayuda.

programme.title: Gold Fever - S21:E09 - Gold, Sweat and Dragon's Blood
programme.desc: Tom and Kia explore a mysterious mine in Colorado.

programme.desc: 語言學博士生Julie幾乎能講你能想像的每種語言。當英俊的Dan聯繫她學法語時，她的生活發生了變化。火花很快擦出 - 這會是他們的完美伴侶嗎？

programme.title: Loving Every Minute
programme.desc: When Stephanie inherits a watch, she learns that it allows her to travel back in time five minutes, once a day. But as she uses it more and more, her life, and romance with her coworker Hunter, doesn't shake out the way she hoped.

programme.title: Threats From The Inside
programme.desc: 布拉德·柯林斯對妻子的愛變成了佔有慾，變得越來越控制。當他懷疑她有外遇時，發生了一場導致悲劇的激烈爭吵。

programme.title: The Royal Bake Off
programme.desc: 當薩馬維亞的皇子來到鎮上尋找皇室麵包師時，麵包師艾莉和瑪莉蓮的對抗更加激烈。當艾莉和皇子產生好感時，似乎他尋找的不僅僅是一個出色的蛋糕。

programme.title: A Match for the Prince
programme.desc: A medieval romance novelist is hired to be a matchmaker for a real-life prince in a desperate attempt to find true love before the fixed royal wedding date.

programme.title: A Bet with the Matchmaker
programme.desc: 一位面临失业的关系专栏作家与一位自称是媒人的人打了个赌，他保证能找到她的完美伴侣。

programme.title: Mommy's Stolen Memories
programme.desc: 馬洛里的生活在她年幼的兒子比利被當地攀岩健身房的一位陌生女子吸引後顛倒過來。比利拒絕透露她說了什麼，並開始行為不端。

programme.title: Secret Lives of College Escorts
programme.desc: 伊芙和朋友偷偷跑去參加派對，但朋友卻不幸喪命，而伊芙也失去了大學獎學金。很快，她找到一份工作以支付學費，但這份工作卻是導致她朋友死亡的危險伴遊計劃的掩護。
